explanation: [0-0] A woman in a purple velvet dress stands in front of an open wooden door. A little boy, holding a steamed bun and crying, stands in front of the camera. Beside the boy, numerous horses carrying banknotes on their backs stand next to him, extending all the way into the doorway. Inside the doorway, a boardwalk is visible, flanked by blue ocean, a blue sky, and white clouds. There are more horses carrying banknotes on the boardwalk. In the distance, a tiger stands on the boardwalk.

[0-5] The woman in purple opens the door, revealing the boardwalk behind it. A crying little boy runs towards the doorway, followed by several horses carrying banknotes, all entering the room. The woman at the doorway gestures in welcome, standing by the door. After entering, the little boy looks back at the horses behind him and continues running toward the camera.
